oNormal">Now, it&#8217;s time to <b>Sign the transaction</b>. This is your digital signature, verifying that it&#8217;s really you making the purchase.</li><li class="MsoNormal">After signing, <b>Approve the transaction</b>. Just one more step to secure your $LUCID tokens!</li><li class="MsoNormal">To spice things up, type in your Telegram username. This will grant you an additional 5% bonus for every user you refer to us. Who said there&#8217;s no such thing as a free lunch?</li><li class="MsoNormal">Finally, copy your referral link from the bottom of the page. Congrats! You&#8217;re all set to start your $LUCID journey and share the excitement with your friends.</li></ol>					</div>
